Project Title: Student Marks and Grade Calculator  
Student Name: Koduru Shiva Sai Krishna  
Year: 2024  
Tools Used: Python, If-Else Conditions, File Handling, Console Input/Output  
Project Type: Solo  
Platform Used: Pydroid 3 (Android)

Description:  
This Python project takes marks for 3 subjects, calculates total and average, assigns a grade, and saves a report to a text file.

Learning Outcome:  
- Python basics  
- Conditional statements  
- File handling  
- Real-world simulation of report generation
